      <title>五角大楼拨款 2.69 亿美元用于军事芯片研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pentagon-doles-out-269-million-for-military-chip-research</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼将向美国 33 个芯片研究项目拨款 2.69 亿美元，这是该计划第二次拨款以支持军方半导体研究。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pentagon-doles-out-269-million-for-military-chip-research</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
