      <title>Uber 将核实乘客身份，以加强驾驶员安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uber-to-verify-passengers-identities-as-part-of-driver-safety-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了让司机感到更安全，Uber Technologies Inc. 将开始根据第三方身份验证数据库检查乘客的账户信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uber-to-verify-passengers-identities-as-part-of-driver-safety-push</guid>
